Invocation Name: ganesh prayers
des:
VoiceTech Labs is happy to launch this app on the occasion of Ganesh Chaturthi, 2021.

This app plays prayers for Lord Ganesh from the Marathi culture in India. Interactively, the app can play one or all prayers from the list below:
1. Ganpati Aarati and Mantra Pushpanjali
2. Atharva Sheersha
3. Heramb Maza Guru Maay Baap
4. Om Namoji Gananayeka
5. Pranyamya Shirasa Devam
6. Ganesh Ekvinshati Naam Stotra
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
